            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E8%83%83%E7%96%BC%E8%83%83%E8%83%80%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E8%83%83%E7%96%BC%E8%83%83%E8%83%80%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常胃疼胃胀建议检测幽门螺杆菌#</span></a>】医生介绍：①幽门螺杆菌是明确的致癌因素之一，易感人群要定期检查；②感染幽门螺杆菌不意味着一定会得胃癌，出现胃癌的比例约1%，无需过度焦虑，应积极配合治疗；③已有家人感染的、经常胃疼胃胀消化不良的，建议重点关注。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%BD%E9%97%A8%E8%9E%BA%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#幽门螺杆菌预防方法#</span></a>有哪些？戳👇🏻（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4901822947852425" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hdzjpfixmkj62eb1cknpd02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XNxVynkwlx085t3DhDWg01041200sAiK0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684257615&amp;ssig=uQ%2Bt3V5B8k&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/kJL6W4AWlx085t3BTvNe01041200eAnI0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684257615&amp;ss